  "2026-04-01T11:59:45.450Z",cursor-agent,Task corresponds to plan workstream A.
  "2026-04-01T12:02:23.059Z",cursor-agent,"Implemented stdin fail-safe behavior: src/core/item/parse.ts now provides actionable Ctrl+D/Ctrl+Z guidance for stdin token errors, and src/cli/commands/beads.ts now fails fast for --file - when stdin is interactive TTY instead of waiting for EOF. Added regressions in tests/unit/parse-utils.spec.ts and tests/unit/beads-command.spec.ts. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/parse-utils.spec.ts tests/unit/beads-command.spec.ts passed (30/30)."
